      "instruction": "<p>While the onion is softening, drain and rinse your <strong>black beans </strong>and <strong>sweetcorn</strong></p><p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]<strong> </span>boiled water</strong></p><p>Once the onion has started to soften, increase the heat to medium-high and add the <strong>drained black beans & sweetcorn </strong>to the pan and cook for 6-7 min or until the corn is charred</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1684831018201-x200.jpg",
