            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>diced red onion</strong>, <strong>diced tomato</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>chilli </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and<strong> chopped coriander</strong> in a bowl</p><p>Add the juice of <strong>half</strong> your <strong>lime[s]</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong>, then stir it all together – this is your<strong> fiery salsa</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1684831026251-x200.jpg",
