            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the corn is charred, add your <strong>tomato paste </strong>and <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan<strong> </strong>with the <strong>vegetable</strong> <strong>stock </strong>and cook for 2-3 min or until it's reduced</p><p>Once done, crush some of the beans with a masher and give everything a good mix up until fully combined – this is your <strong>plant-based black bean & corn</strong></p>",
