    {
      "instruction": "<p>Spread your <strong>smashed avocado </strong>over the <strong>warmed tortillas</strong></p><p>Top with the <strong>plant-based black bean & corn </strong>and <strong>fiery salsa</strong></p><p>Garnish with a <strong>lime wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
